title: The Chaser Decides 2004
description:
(Taken from http://www.abc.net.au/tv/chaser/about.htm)

As with the ground-breaking 2001 series &#039;The Election Chaser&#039;, The Chaser Decides features a panel of top political commentators, led by Craig Reucassel and Chris Taylor (Triple J Drive) with expert analysis from Julian Morrow and Andrew Hansen. Charles Firth, Chas Licciardello and Dominic Knight will again report from the field right across Australia.

The Chaser Decides - election 2004
The Chaser team cover the Australian federal election of 2004

Four episodes -

i) 23rd September 2004
ii) 30th September 2004
iii) 7th October 2004
iv) 14th October 2004
